Package gameClient

Class Agent

java.lang.Object
gameClient.Agent
public class Agent
extends java.lang.Object
This class is a representation of agent in the Pokemons Game. most of the data are coming from the server as Json, and there data that coming from the client, like _curr_fruit, current path, and the graph.
